data.description: This Adorable Ranch home is Cute and Cozy..... 3 bedrooms/1 full bath, nice open living room and dining area....which leads you to the kitchen and utility room.  All on ONE level and perfect for someone with small kids or someone who does not want to climb stairs.  This Cute house is sitting on a nice flat usable lot. Located in the Waynesville RVI school district.  Walking distance to the Middle School.....approximately 10 minutes from the West gate of Fort Leonard Wood.
